Maintainer: Joris Mulder <j.mulder3@tilburguniversity.edu>
Description: Empirical and simulated data for relational event analyses. Each dataset consists of an edgelist - the sequence events representing the link sent from one actor to another at a particular timepoint; and a dataframe describing the actors and their attributes if present. 
